Unnecessary diagnostic tests.

 X-ray, laboratory, and pathological services and machine diagnostic tests not related to a specific illness or injury
or a definitive set of symptoms except for cancer screening mammography and cancer screening papanicolaou (PAP)
tests provided under the terms and conditions contained in the guidelines adopted by the Director, OCHAMPUS.



